graph TD
    subgraph Data Ingestion (Upsert)
    A[Raw Text Document] --> B[Embedding Model]
    B -->|Translates to 1536-dim Vector| C[{Vector + Metadata JSON}]
    C -->|Upsert API| D[(Pinecone Database)]
    end
    
    subgraph Retrieval (Query)
    E[User Question] --> F[Embedding Model]
    F -->|Translates to 1536-dim Vector| G[Query Vector]
    G -->|Cosine Similarity Search + Metadata Filter| D
    D -->|Returns Top-K Matches| H[Relevant Context]
    end
    
    %% Styling
    classDef db fill:#f9f,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px;
    class D db;
